00:52:18.846 --> 00:52:20.210 align:middle line:90%
Thyroid disease.

00:52:20.210 --> 00:52:23.900 align:middle line:84%
So many women have some
kind of thyroid problem.

00:52:23.900 --> 00:52:26.600 align:middle line:84%
And I want to address
this holistically.

00:52:26.600 --> 00:52:30.110 align:middle line:84%
First of all, over the
last 30 years or so,

00:52:30.110 --> 00:52:34.460 align:middle line:84%
they have replaced iodides in
bread-making with bromides.

00:52:34.460 --> 00:52:37.370 align:middle line:84%
Bromides are a halogen.
Chlorine in the water

00:52:37.370 --> 00:52:40.190 align:middle line:84%
is a halogen. Fluoride in
the water is a halogen.

00:52:40.190 --> 00:52:42.050 align:middle line:84%
And all of these
halogens-- if you

00:52:42.050 --> 00:52:44.870 align:middle line:84%
look at the periodic table
of elements in chemistry,

00:52:44.870 --> 00:52:49.100 align:middle line:84%
you will see that iodine,
which is absolutely necessary

00:52:49.100 --> 00:52:53.150 align:middle line:84%
for full thyroid function, and
by the way, for breast health

00:52:53.150 --> 00:52:58.790 align:middle line:84%
and for ovarian health,
that these halogens actually

00:52:58.790 --> 00:53:01.615 align:middle line:84%
displace the iodine
from the cells.

00:53:01.615 --> 00:53:07.010 align:middle line:84%
So we have in many places
in the world a deficiency

00:53:07.010 --> 00:53:12.560 align:middle line:84%
or at least a sub-optimal
level of iodine in the diet

00:53:12.560 --> 00:53:13.530 align:middle line:90%
and in the body.

00:53:13.530 --> 00:53:15.650 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, I'd like
to make the distinction

00:53:15.650 --> 00:53:17.900 align:middle line:84%
between gross deficiency
disease, which

00:53:17.900 --> 00:53:19.910 align:middle line:90%
in iodine would be a goiter.

00:53:19.910 --> 00:53:25.190 align:middle line:84%
This is big thyroid
tumor and constant breast

00:53:25.190 --> 00:53:29.660 align:middle line:84%
pain, which would be because of
sub-optimal levels of iodine.

00:53:29.660 --> 00:53:34.730 align:middle line:84%
By the way, breast tissue
actively sequesters iodine.

00:53:34.730 --> 00:53:36.550 align:middle line:84%
And one of the ways
for anyone listening

00:53:36.550 --> 00:53:40.940 align:middle line:84%
who has that "misnomer
fibrocystic breast disease,"

00:53:40.940 --> 00:53:42.590 align:middle line:90%
start taking kelp tablets.

00:53:42.590 --> 00:53:43.550 align:middle line:90%
You'll get rid of it.

00:53:43.550 --> 00:53:45.980 align:middle line:84%
So iodine is very,
very important

00:53:45.980 --> 00:53:48.580 align:middle line:84%
for the health of the thyroid
and the health of breasts.

00:53:48.580 --> 00:53:51.710 align:middle line:84%
And it's the first thing
I would give to a woman

00:53:51.710 --> 00:53:54.530 align:middle line:84%
who's been diagnosed
with thyroid problems

00:53:54.530 --> 00:53:57.748 align:middle line:84%
or who thinks that she might
have a thyroid problem.

00:53:57.748 --> 00:53:58.790 align:middle line:90%
Now, here's what happens.

00:53:58.790 --> 00:54:03.650 align:middle line:84%
When women begin to first
take increased iodine,

00:54:03.650 --> 00:54:07.200 align:middle line:84%
all those toxic halogens
come up out of their cells.

00:54:07.200 --> 00:54:09.020 align:middle line:90%
They get a skin rash, usually.

00:54:09.020 --> 00:54:10.070 align:middle line:90%
And what do they say?

00:54:10.070 --> 00:54:11.630 align:middle line:90%
I'm "allergic to iodine."

00:54:11.630 --> 00:54:12.620 align:middle line:90%
That's not it.

00:54:12.620 --> 00:54:15.120 align:middle line:90%
They're detoxing their body.

00:54:15.120 --> 00:54:16.560 align:middle line:90%
And so that often happens.

00:54:16.560 --> 00:54:19.670 align:middle line:84%
The other thing is when you do
thyroid function test, the TSH,

00:54:19.670 --> 00:54:21.620 align:middle line:90%
thyroid-stimulating hormone--

00:54:21.620 --> 00:54:23.900 align:middle line:90%
needs to be less than 3.

00:54:23.900 --> 00:54:29.120 align:middle line:84%
And in many of the labs, the
indices for thyroid for TSH

00:54:29.120 --> 00:54:30.330 align:middle line:90%
are too high.

00:54:30.330 --> 00:54:35.840 align:middle line:84%
So the woman will actually have
sub-clinical hypothyroidism.

00:54:35.840 --> 00:54:40.280 align:middle line:84%
And if you really know that
it needs to be less than 3,

00:54:40.280 --> 00:54:41.960 align:middle line:84%
then you're going to
start treating it.

00:54:41.960 --> 00:54:44.180 align:middle line:84%
But the way to treat
it is not necessarily

00:54:44.180 --> 00:54:46.250 align:middle line:90%
with synthetic thyroid.

00:54:46.250 --> 00:54:48.150 align:middle line:90%
Start treating it holistically.

00:54:48.150 --> 00:54:49.470 align:middle line:90%
And then one more thing.

00:54:49.470 --> 00:54:51.410 align:middle line:90%
There is the iodide thing.

00:54:51.410 --> 00:54:53.390 align:middle line:90%
But then there's-- what is this?

00:54:53.390 --> 00:54:54.950 align:middle line:90%
It's the fifth chakra.

00:54:54.950 --> 00:54:56.300 align:middle line:90%
It's your voice.

00:54:56.300 --> 00:54:58.230 align:middle line:90%
It's having your say.

00:54:58.230 --> 00:55:02.510 align:middle line:84%
For 5,000 years,
the feminine voice

00:55:02.510 --> 00:55:05.030 align:middle line:90%
has been actively squelched.

00:55:05.030 --> 00:55:07.290 align:middle line:84%
There's a wonderful quote
from physicist John Wheeler

00:55:07.290 --> 00:55:08.090 align:middle line:90%
that I love.

00:55:08.090 --> 00:55:09.005 align:middle line:90%
And it's this.

00:55:09.005 --> 00:55:12.440 align:middle line:84%
"Masculinity expresses
the idea that there

00:55:12.440 --> 00:55:15.020 align:middle line:90%
are things worth dying for.

00:55:15.020 --> 00:55:18.230 align:middle line:84%
Femininity expresses
the idea that there

00:55:18.230 --> 00:55:21.340 align:middle line:90%
are things worth living for."

00:55:21.340 --> 00:55:23.000 align:middle line:84%
And what's happening
now on planet

00:55:23.000 --> 00:55:26.615 align:middle line:84%
Earth is the feminine energy
in men and women is rising.

00:55:26.615 --> 00:55:27.740 align:middle line:90%
How many wars can we fight?

00:55:27.740 --> 00:55:31.310 align:middle line:84%
How many people who don't
agree with us can we kill?

00:55:31.310 --> 00:55:34.220 align:middle line:84%
We realized through the
internet, which is probably

00:55:34.220 --> 00:55:37.070 align:middle line:84%
what changed Egyptian
politics, was

00:55:37.070 --> 00:55:42.050 align:middle line:84%
Facebook, that we are in
fact one small planet.

00:55:42.050 --> 00:55:45.100 align:middle line:84%
And we can't be killing off
everything that we don't want.

00:55:45.100 --> 00:55:49.130 align:middle line:84%
So the feminine
values are rising up.

00:55:49.130 --> 00:55:51.260 align:middle line:90%
And what do women do?

00:55:51.260 --> 00:55:53.730 align:middle line:84%
Women are the ones
typically who do

00:55:53.730 --> 00:55:56.450 align:middle line:84%
the birthday parties,
the celebrations,

00:55:56.450 --> 00:55:59.900 align:middle line:84%
making things pretty,
putting the little note

00:55:59.900 --> 00:56:03.920 align:middle line:84%
in the lunchbox, things
worth living for.

00:56:03.920 --> 00:56:08.630 align:middle line:84%
Dancing, pleasure, love,
color, wanting to look good

00:56:08.630 --> 00:56:09.950 align:middle line:90%
on your skin and your hair.

00:56:09.950 --> 00:56:13.410 align:middle line:84%
Nothing wrong with
the feminine values.

00:56:13.410 --> 00:56:16.310 align:middle line:84%
But when you have
said as a woman--

00:56:16.310 --> 00:56:20.750 align:middle line:84%
for most have written human
history what you thought--

00:56:20.750 --> 00:56:23.000 align:middle line:90%
it didn't go over too well.

00:56:23.000 --> 00:56:29.030 align:middle line:84%
And so many women have squelched
their own voice for fear

00:56:29.030 --> 00:56:31.190 align:middle line:84%
that they would be
killed, or for fear

00:56:31.190 --> 00:56:33.620 align:middle line:84%
that they would be shunned,
or that they would be alone.

00:56:33.620 --> 00:56:37.550 align:middle line:84%
That if I have my say and I
really say what I'm thinking,

00:56:37.550 --> 00:56:39.690 align:middle line:90%
I'll be alone.

00:56:39.690 --> 00:56:41.690 align:middle line:84%
And because we need each
other and because we're

00:56:41.690 --> 00:56:45.900 align:middle line:84%
a tribe culture and
a tribe species,

00:56:45.900 --> 00:56:47.630 align:middle line:90%
we don't want to risk that.

00:56:47.630 --> 00:56:50.180 align:middle line:84%
So we have squelched
what we want to say.

00:56:50.180 --> 00:56:52.340 align:middle line:90%
What are canker sores?

00:56:52.340 --> 00:56:54.110 align:middle line:90%
Aphthous ulcers.

00:56:54.110 --> 00:56:56.240 align:middle line:84%
They're things that you
